        <item>
            <title>《MHW》PS5 Pro vs PS5 大比拚，值得為芒亨升級 PS5 Pro？</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/28/ps5-pro-vs-ps5-mhw/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=ps5-pro-vs-ps5-mhw</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/28/ps5-pro-vs-ps5-mhw/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 15:36:33 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[遊戲情報]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1294804</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>《Monster Hunter Wilds》正式推出，相信好多朋友都準備為此大作做好準備，包括是否適合在這個時候升級 PS5 Pro。在正式版本中，PS5 Pro 專用的畫質提升功能正式引入，在早前測試版我們還未能作出結論，但今次正式版我們終可正式來比較一下。總括來説，PS5 與 PS5 Pro 在畫質、光影效果及整體流暢度方面均存在明顯差距，如果用家希望在 PlayStation 平台享受本作，不打算 DIY 砌機電腦的話，就可留意以下介紹，考慮 PS5 Pro 購入的可能性。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294872" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05186-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05186-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05186.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>測試影片：</h2><p><iframe loading="lazy" style="border: none; overflow: hidden;" src="https://www.facebook.com/plugins/video.php?height=476&amp;href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Funwirehk%2Fvideos%2F3969945699943116%2F&amp;show_text=false&amp;width=267&amp;t=0" width="500" height="776" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe><br />
&nbsp;</p><h2>三種模式該如何選擇？</h2><p>《Monster Hunter Wilds》的 PlayStation 5 版本共提供三種模式，分別為：</p><ul><li>「幀率優先」模式：以穩定幀率為主要目標</li><li>「解析度優先」模式：全力提升畫面解析度</li><li>「重視平衡」模式：在畫面與幀率之間取得折衷</li></ul><p>雖然三個模式在 PS5 及 PS5 Pro 上的名稱與功能一致，但實際體驗卻存在極大差異。尤其當畫面細節、光影效果及幀率穩定性一併比較時，PS5 Pro 的優勢更為顯著。以下將會慢慢講解。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294875" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05194-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05194-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05194.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Monster Hunter Wild 顯示設定</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294877" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05193-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05193-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05193.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲內有 3 個模式：解析度優先、重視平衡、幀率優先</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294878" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05195-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05195-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05195.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲另外亦有 120Hz 更新率輸出支援（留意並不是指 120fps 進行遊戲），在 PS5 Pro 上可獲得更為流暢的畫面</p><h2>「幀率優先」模式：<b>PS5 Pro </b>兼顧畫質與流暢，<b>PS5 </b>僅能求穩</h2><p>顧名思義，「幀率優先」以優先確保穩定幀率為核心目標，兩部主機均以 60fps 為目標。然而 PS5 Pro 與 PS5 之間的畫面表現差距，在此模式已經非常明顯。PS5 Pro 在該模式下幾乎可全程維持 60fps，即使場景複雜，窒畫面（突然大幅明顯幀數下降）情況亦極少發生。這方面玩家可以放心進行遊戲。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294879" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05191-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05191-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05191.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>例子 1：</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294811" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025022895323-694x388.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025022895323-694x388.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025022895323-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲測試場景（圖為 PS5 Pro 幀率優先模式）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294809" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ps5_pro_-657x580.jpg" alt="" width="657" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ps5_pro_-657x580.jpg 657w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ps5_pro_.jpg 922w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 657px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294810" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ps5_2-614x580.jpg" alt="" width="614" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ps5_2-614x580.jpg 614w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ps5_2.jpg 792w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 614px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲對比之下，樹木的溝造以及角色背後的紋理，都是 PS5 Pro 清楚得多</p><p>畫質方面，PS5 採用動態解析度（Dynamic Resolution Scaling, DRS）技術，內部渲染範圍約在 720p 至 1080p，通過空間升頻和後期鋭化處理輸出到 4K 顯示器。而 PS5 Pro 最大優勢在於其具備 PSSR（PlayStation Spectral Super Resolution）技術輔助，透過 AI 升頻技術有效提升畫面清晰度，即使渲染解像度僅為 1080p，經 PSSR 處理後整體畫面依然清晰乾淨。無論是樹葉邊緣、角色細節，還是遠方地形紋理，均比 PS5 清楚許多，且樹葉閃爍與鋸齒問題大幅減少。</p><p>相較之下，PS5 雖然同樣以 60fps 為目標，但面對較為複雜場景，例如大量魔物同時出現，或大面積水面反射時，幀率偶爾會下降至 50 幾 fps。</p><p>例子 2：</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294812" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025022895945-694x388.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025022895945-694x388.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025022895945-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲測試場景（圖為 PS5 Pro 幀率優先模式）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294813" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_9_59_452-608x580.jpg" alt="" width="608" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_9_59_452-608x580.jpg 608w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_9_59_452.jpg 904w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 608px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294815" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_10_00_102-1-540x580.jpg" alt="" width="540" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_10_00_102-1-540x580.jpg 540w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_10_00_102-1.jpg 814w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 540px" /></p><h2>遊玩體驗比較</h2><p>PS5 整體畫面較為粗糙，遠景物件輪廓模糊，尤其是沙漠場景中，沙地與岩石顏色相近，畫面鋭利度不足，導致玩家需要額外花時間辨認場景中的關鍵物件，對戰鬥專注度造成一定影響。</p><h2>「解析度優先」模式：<b>PS5 Pro </b>畫質細緻突出，<b>PS5 </b>畫面模糊難辨</h2><p>這個模式是以展現遊戲最高畫質為目標。所以不論是 PS5 Pro 或者 PS5，都未能達到有 60fps 或以上的水平。對偏愛華麗畫面的玩家來説，「解析度優先」模式無疑是畫質愛好者的首選。在此模式下 PS5 Pro 與 PS5 之間的畫質差距更為顯著。PS5 Pro 的解析度最高可達 1944p，並同樣透過 PSSR 提升畫面整體細節表現，無論近景或遠景均能保持極高畫質。岩石表面紋理、鎧甲反光質感、以及樹葉層次感，均明顯優於 PS5。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294880" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05193-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05193-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05193-1.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>例子 1：</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294816" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228100553-694x388.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228100553-694x388.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228100553-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲測試場景（圖為 PS5 Pro 解析度優先模式）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294833" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_10_05_532-2-613x580.jpg" alt="" width="613" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_10_05_532-2-613x580.jpg 613w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_10_05_532-2.jpg 940w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 613px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294835" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_10_06_18-1-567x580.jpg" alt="" width="567" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_10_06_18-1-567x580.jpg 567w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_10_06_18-1.jpg 880w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 567px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲比對主角背後，PS5 Pro 解析度優先模式的畫面清晰得多</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294837" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/202502283_10_05_532-694x435.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="435" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/202502283_10_05_532-694x435.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/202502283_10_05_532.jpg 1018w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294838" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_10_06_18-2-694x397.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="397" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_10_06_18-2-694x397.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_10_06_18-2.jpg 1086w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲遠景景物也看到，PS5 Pro 懸崖邊的紋理詳細得多</p><p>相反 PS5 版本的動態解像度僅有 1080p 至 1440p 之間，加上缺少 PSSR，只能依賴傳統空間升頻（Spatial Upscaling）及後期鋭化處理。整體畫面較為柔和，甚至帶有明顯有一層「油膜」的感覺，樹葉與場景物件邊緣閃爍與鋸齒問題在複雜場景中特別嚴重。</p><p>光影效果方面，PS5 Pro 在此模式下具備光線追蹤（Ray Tracing）反射技術，水面光影反射效果更具層次感，水面看上去更加通透。特別是敵人經過水面時，會有明顯很清晰的反射效果。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294840" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_10_33_192-694x388.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_10_33_192-694x388.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_10_33_192-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲PS5 Pro 解析度優先模式，看到的水面波紋漣漪都會較豐富，最大分別是敵人走過水面會產生倒影</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294839" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/202502228_10_37_13-694x388.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/202502228_10_37_13-694x388.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/202502228_10_37_13-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲PS5 解析度優先模式中，敵人走過倒影會十分淺，很難察覺（只有影子是一樣的）看到的水面波紋漣漪都會較少，清澈度較低</p><p>反觀 PS5，只能使用螢幕空間反射（SSR），不僅反射內容不完整，且畫面細節模糊，感覺上水面會較為「污濁」。當部分反射面被遮擋時，倒影直接消失，敵人經過水面時反射效果也不特別明顯，整體畫面效果略顯粗糙。</p><h2>遊玩體驗比較</h2><p>畫質提升的代價便是流暢度明顯下降。「解析度優先」模式之下，PS5 Pro 的體感幀率約為 30fps，即使 PS5 Pro 亦無法避免。角色移動、翻滾、攻擊等操作皆明顯失去流暢感，尤其面對高機動性魔物時，操作遲滯感格外明顯。相信很多玩家都未必願意在這樣的流暢度下長期遊玩。</p><h2>「重視平衡」模式：<b>PS5 Pro </b>表現均衡，<b>PS5 </b>勉強堪用</h2><p>「重視平衡」模式，為希望在畫質與效能之間取得平衡的玩家而設，PS5 Pro 在此模式下的整體表現令人驚喜。PS5 Pro 該模式的解析度約為 1440p，經 PSSR 升頻後，畫面質感接近 「解析度優先」模式，約七成的水平。同時亦保留部分光線追蹤反射效果。幀率目標為 40fps。至於 PS5，「重視平衡」模式的整體表現則略顯尷尬。畫質僅相當於 「解析度優先」模式，約五成水準，光線追蹤反射功能完全取消，畫面整體質感僅稍優於「幀率優先」模式。然而由於缺少 PSSR，畫面仍偏柔和，細節表現一般。幀率目標為 40fps，但複雜場景時會降至 30fps 以下。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294881" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05192-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05192-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05192.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294857" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_11_08_532-694x388.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_11_08_532-694x388.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_11_08_532-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294858" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_11_09_182-694x388.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_11_09_182-694x388.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_11_09_182-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲PS5 Pro 平衡模式較為精細</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294847" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_10_56_192-694x388.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_10_56_192-694x388.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_10_56_192-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294854" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_11_02_192-694x388.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_11_02_192-694x388.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_11_02_192-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲PS5 平衡模式畫面會較為柔和，而且流暢度會略遜於 PS5 Pro</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1294855" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_11_04_082-685x580.jpg" alt="" width="469" height="397" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_11_04_082-685x580.jpg 685w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_11_04_082.jpg 1063w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 469px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1294856" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_211_05_31-691x580.jpg" alt="" width="449" height="377" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_211_05_31-691x580.jpg 691w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_211_05_31.jpg 924w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 449px" /></p><h2>遊玩體驗比較</h2><p>PS5 Pro 的平衡模式十分可取，整體流暢度明顯優於 「解析度優先」模式。雖然不及「幀率優先」模式順暢，但整體戰鬥體驗依然屬於可接受範圍。偶爾出現掉幀，但對節奏影響不大。PS5 方面角色操作流暢度亦明顯不如 「幀率優先」模式，整體戰鬥體驗僅屬堪用等級。</p><h2>總結：<b>PS5 Pro </b>全方位壓倒<b> PS5</b></h2><p>綜合三個模式比較，PS5 Pro 在《Monster Hunter Wilds》中的表現，無論畫質、光影效果、還是幀率穩定性，皆明顯優於 PS5。尤其光線追蹤反射的加入，讓場景真實感與沉浸感大幅提升，整體遊玩體驗更趨近於進入《Monster Hunter》世界的冒險旅程。</p><p>相對而言，PS5 玩家則需調整預期，若選擇 「幀率優先」模式，尚可保有流暢戰鬥體驗，但若貪圖畫質選擇其他模式，畫面模糊、細節缺失、反射效果不佳等問題，將直接影響整體狩獵體驗。當場景內魔物數量增多或特效集中時，畫面混亂且難以辨識敵我，整體操作手感亦明顯不如 Pro 版。</p><table style="width: 100%;" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tbody><tr><td style="border-color: #d2d2fc; background-color: #d7fcf7; width: 17.317487%;" valign="top"><strong>模式</strong></td><td style="background-color: #ffe3e3; width: 12.393888%;" valign="top"><strong>解像度（動態）</strong></td><td style="background-color: #e8ffe9; width: 22.071307%;" valign="top"><strong>畫質</strong></td><td style="background-color: #fffedb; width: 8.064516%;" valign="top"><strong>反射效果</strong></td><td style="width: 5.432937%; background-color: #ebf7f7;" valign="top"><strong>目標幀率</strong></td><td style="width: 5.517827%; background-color: #f0dae2;" valign="top"><strong>真實體感</strong></td><td style="width: 29.117148%;" valign="top"><strong>遊玩體驗評語</strong></td></tr><tr><td style="border-color: #d2d2fc; background-color: #d7fcf7; width: 17.317487%;" valign="top">「幀率優先」模式, PS5 Pro</td><td style="background-color: #ffe3e3; width: 12.393888%;" valign="top">約 1080p + PSSR</td><td style="background-color: #e8ffe9; width: 22.071307%;" valign="top">清晰，邊緣平滑，少閃爍</td><td style="background-color: #fffedb; width: 8.064516%;" valign="top">SSR</td><td style="width: 5.432937%; background-color: #ebf7f7;" valign="top">60fps</td><td style="width: 5.517827%; background-color: #f0dae2;" valign="top">55-60fps</td><td style="width: 29.117148%;" valign="top">畫面乾淨又順暢，最佳選擇之一</td></tr><tr><td style="border-color: #d2d2fc; background-color: #d7fcf7; width: 17.317487%;" valign="top">「幀率優先」模式, PS5</td><td style="background-color: #ffe3e3; width: 12.393888%;" valign="top">約 720-1080p</td><td style="background-color: #e8ffe9; width: 22.071307%;" valign="top">偏柔，鋸齒明顯，遠景模糊</td><td style="background-color: #fffedb; width: 8.064516%;" valign="top">SSR</td><td style="width: 5.432937%; background-color: #ebf7f7;" valign="top">60fps</td><td style="width: 5.517827%; background-color: #f0dae2;" valign="top">50-60fps</td><td style="width: 29.117148%;" valign="top">畫質普通，但操作感順暢，PS5 唯一推介</td></tr><tr><td style="border-color: #d2d2fc; background-color: #d7fcf7; width: 17.317487%;" valign="top">「重視平衡」模式, PS5 Pro</td><td style="background-color: #ffe3e3; width: 12.393888%;" valign="top">約 1440p + PSSR</td><td style="background-color: #e8ffe9; width: 22.071307%;" valign="top">近似 7 成 Resolution Mode 質感</td><td style="background-color: #fffedb; width: 8.064516%;" valign="top">光線追蹤反射</td><td style="width: 5.432937%; background-color: #ebf7f7;" valign="top">40fps</td><td style="width: 5.517827%; background-color: #f0dae2;" valign="top">35-40fps</td><td style="width: 29.117148%;" valign="top">兼顧畫質與流暢，適合鍾意靚畫面又怕太 LAG 玩家</td></tr><tr><td style="border-color: #d2d2fc; background-color: #d7fcf7; width: 17.317487%;" valign="top">「重視平衡」模式, PS5</td><td style="background-color: #ffe3e3; width: 12.393888%;" valign="top">約 1080p</td><td style="background-color: #e8ffe9; width: 22.071307%;" valign="top">解析度比 Frame Rate 高少少，但偏朦</td><td style="background-color: #fffedb; width: 8.064516%;" valign="top">SSR</td><td style="width: 5.432937%; background-color: #ebf7f7;" valign="top">40fps</td><td style="width: 5.517827%; background-color: #f0dae2;" valign="top">30-40fps</td><td style="width: 29.117148%;" valign="top">畫質普通，流暢度麻麻，冇乜優勢</td></tr><tr><td style="border-color: #d2d2fc; background-color: #d7fcf7; width: 17.317487%;" valign="top">「解析度優先」模式, PS5 Pro</td><td style="background-color: #ffe3e3; width: 12.393888%;" valign="top">1728p-1944p + PSSR</td><td style="background-color: #e8ffe9; width: 22.071307%;" valign="top">最高清細緻</td><td style="background-color: #fffedb; width: 8.064516%;" valign="top">光線追蹤反射</td><td style="width: 5.432937%; background-color: #ebf7f7;" valign="top">30fps</td><td style="width: 5.517827%; background-color: #f0dae2;" valign="top">28-30fps</td><td style="width: 29.117148%;" valign="top">畫面超靚，但操作感變重，適合影相黨</td></tr><tr><td style="border-color: #d2d2fc; background-color: #d7fcf7; width: 17.317487%;" valign="top">「解析度優先」模式, PS5</td><td style="background-color: #ffe3e3; width: 12.393888%;" valign="top">1080p-1440p</td><td style="background-color: #e8ffe9; width: 22.071307%;" valign="top">偏柔偏朦，細節不清</td><td style="background-color: #fffedb; width: 8.064516%;" valign="top">SSR</td><td style="width: 5.432937%; background-color: #ebf7f7;" valign="top">30fps</td><td style="width: 5.517827%; background-color: #f0dae2;" valign="top">25-30fps</td><td style="width: 29.117148%;" valign="top">影相都嫌唔夠靚，操作仲唔順，唔推</td></tr></tbody></table><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294882" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05190-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05190-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05190.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲今次由 ROG 借出電競熒幕 ROG Swift OLED PG32UCDM 試玩 MHW。這個熒幕具有 4K 解像度的 32 吋超大畫面，用上 OLED 技術畫面對比度真的無得彈，0.03ms(GTG)、240Hz 更新率駁高階電腦打機更爽快，當然無論駁 PS5 或者電腦都同樣合適。官方建議零售價：HK$12,499</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/02/28/ps5-pro-vs-ps5-mhw/game-channel/">《MHW》PS5 Pro vs PS5 大比拚，值得為芒亨升級 PS5 Pro？</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
